Nigeria Maiduguri City Blast Death Toll Rises to 14, 7 Arrests, Police Say

-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 
2011-06-08T16:29:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/nigeria-maiduguri-city-blast-death-toll-rises-to-14-7-arrests-police-say.html
The death toll following three blasts
in the northeastern Nigerian city of Maiduguri rose to 14, with
17 people seriously wounded, Borno state police spokesman Lawal
Abdullahi said.  Seven people have been arrested in connection with the
explosions that took place yesterday, Abdullahi said by phone
from Maiduguri today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisha Bala-Gbogbo in Abuja at 
